      <p begin="01:58.230" end="02:01.830" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="01:58.230" end="01:58.870">思</span><span begin="01:58.870" end="01:59.150">い</span><span begin="01:59.150" end="01:59.450">出</span><span begin="01:59.450" end="01:59.790">だ</span><span begin="01:59.790" end="01:59.970">っ</span><span begin="02:00.070" end="02:00.390">た</span><span begin="02:00.390" end="02:00.660">り</span><span begin="02:00.660" end="02:00.970">全</span><span begin="02:00.970" end="02:01.280">部</span><span begin="02:01.280" end="02:01.610">全</span><span begin="02:01.610" end="02:01.830">部</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">可能是回忆全部全部</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Omoide dattari zenbu zenbu</span></p>
